         fortunes-flashrider
Description: Collection of basic command line tools
 This meta-package installs extra command line tools on the system.
 .
 These are:
 - coreutils-nano (coreutils with progressbar patch)
 - BashStyle-NG
 - vim
 - gpm
 - less
 - rsync
 - bash
 - bash-completion
 - shc
 - dcfldd
 - fortunes-flashrider

